\v 28 YÉØ jĆ¤y ajcxy huÉØdibÉØ meetzcÉØxp, huen ixmajtzcÉØxy meedzÉØÉØ, etz ijxtĆ¤huÉØpy ytung. Co ytunÉØpy ma cÉØ'mdung jĆ«bÉØ pubedÉØpy ajcxy ymÉØgĆ¼gtÉØjc huÉØdibÉØ yajmayjajtcÉØxp tijaty. 
